      "content": "wait caffeine?? wont that make me more dehydrated or make my heart race? i'm already feeling a bit shaky. i just feel so out of it, like i'm not really present. is it really just a \"fog\" or should i be worried about something more serious like a stroke? you seem pretty sure it's just the heat tho.",
